    <subfield code="y">00001 This plot shows the parameter $r$ as a function of the scalar spectral index $n_s$ for two values of the constant $\alpha$, i. e. $\alpha = 0.2$ (solid line) and $\alpha = 0.8$ (dashed line). The values of $r$ have been normalized in such a way that we have $r=0$ when $n_s = 1$.</subfield>
